      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2 per project scoping decision.",
      "rationale": "Statistical characterization of test sample variability was not required at MRL 2. A single pump unit representative of nominal manufacturing tolerances was used for all in-vitro validation runs."
